---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Legal Notice | Théo" lang="en" description="Legal notice and privacy policy for Théo DULUARD's portfolio — GDPR data processing information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-100">Legal Notice & Personal Data</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">1. Site publisher</h2>
        <p>This website is published by Théo DULUARD, software engineer (apprenticeship).</p>
        <p>Hosting: GitHub Pages</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-4 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">2. Automatically collected technical data</h2>
        <p>
          Technical data is automatically collected on each visit on the basis of the <strong>legitimate interest</strong> of the data controller, in accordance with <strong>Article 6.1.f of the GDPR</strong>, for anonymous audience statistics purposes.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Data collected</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-slate-400">
          <li>Browser and operating system</li>
          <li>Device type (desktop, mobile, tablet)</li>
          <li>Screen resolution and viewport size</li>
          <li>Preferred browser language</li>
          <li>Timezone, country and city of origin (estimated via IP address)</li>
          <li>Page visited and traffic source (referrer)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Purpose and retention</h3>
        <p>This data is used to understand portfolio audience patterns (devices used, visitor countries, traffic sources) without personal identification. It is retained for <strong>12 months</strong> and is not shared with any third party. No advertising tracking cookies are used.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-200 mt-6 mb-2">Right to object</h3>
        <p>You may object to this processing at any time by contacting me via LinkedIn. Your request will be handled promptly.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
